data.description: Looking for a home that is in a remote location then this is the HOME FOR YOU!!! This  modular home is on a permanent foundation and features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathroom and a detached 3 car garage with 2,280SQFT....of spacious living for you and the family and all on 2.51 Acres of land. This property does need some TLC and requires some attention, maintenance, and renovations but the renovations can be rewarding in turning this property into the HOME OF YOUR DREAMS!!!!
